sagex.phoenix.progress

Class ProgressTracker<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • sagex.phoenix.progress.ProgressTracker<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IProgressMonitor

    public class ProgressTracker<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IProgressMonitor
    A progress tracker is a special kind of IProgressMonitor that will track the status of items as success, failed, or skipped.
